data.description: Priced to Sell.  Single Story Residence located on a cut-de-sac. Spacious living room, separate family area off kitchen area. Laundry room and storage located inside.  Three spacious bedrooms with owner's on-suite. Newer A/C and heating. Roof replaced. Large sliding glass door open to the back yard with covered patio. Back yard has privacy. Detached large two car garage is at the end of a long driveway.  Storage shed is behind garage is included.
